<para style="p">A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Judge me, Yahweh, for I have walked with integrity;</para>

<para style="q1">I have trusted in Yahweh without wavering.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Examine me, Yahweh, and test me;</para>

<para style="q1">test the purity of my inner parts and my heart!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />For your covenant faithfulness is before my eyes,</para>

<para style="q1">and I walk about in your faithfulness.</para>
